<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ABM users API with JSON WEB TOKEN  - Home</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.3.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-SzlrxWUlpfuzQ+pcUCosxcglQRNAq/DZjVsC0lE40xsADsfeQoEypE+enwcOiGjk/bSuGGKHEyjSoQ1zVisanQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
</head>
<body>
        <% if (user) { %>
        <%- include('partials/headerUser') %>  
        <% } else { %>
        <%- include('partials/headerVisitor') %>  
        <% } %>
    
         <div class="container m-auto p-5">
            <h1 class="mb-5">API End points</h1>
            <div class="w-100">
                <p><strong>GET</strong> index: <a href="http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/" target="_blank">http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/</a></p>
                <p><strong>GET</strong> All Users: <a href="http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users" target="_blank">http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users</a></p>
                <p><strong>GET</strong> Find User by ID: <a href="http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users/1" target="_blank">http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users/1 (example)</a></p>
                <p><strong>GET</strong> Find User by specific field: <a href="http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users/name/juan" target="_blank">http://<%= hostName %><%= port %>/api/users/name/juan (example)</a></p>
                <p><strong>POST</strong> <%= hostName %>/api/users/ (example) with <strong>JSON DATA</strong> in body request - 'name' and 'email' should be unique</p>
                <p><strong>PATCH</strong> <%= hostName %>/api/users/67 (example) Existing id user in DB and <strong>JSON DATA</strong> in body request</p>
                <p>example:
                <code>{
                    "name" : "nuevo_luis", 
                    "email" : "nuevo.luisito@hotmail.com",
                    "password" : 1234,
                    "roles_id" : 1,
                    "photos_id" : 2,
                    "real_name" : "Luis Beltran",  
                    "birthday" : "1901-03-05", 
                    "palettes_id" : 1
                }</code>
                </p>
                <p><strong>DELETE</strong> <%= hostName %>:1000/api/users/67 (example) Existing id user in DB</p>
            </div>
        </div>    

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>